data.description: Welcome to the Tiki Penthouse!  This 3 bedroom bungalow is just a mile from the beach, minutes from the Strand and has a clear view of the cruise ships in the intercoastal canal! Surrounded by tall tropical palms, this Island paradise is sure to rejuvenate your soul. Mix a drink and enjoy the ocean breeze underneath the palapa or relax in the hot tub while watching a movie on the outdoor projector screen! Then take the elevator upstairs and inside to watch TV equipped with full surround sound.  The kitchen is open to the living and dining area, so it's just as perfect for entertaining inside as it is out!  Kitchen has newer, built in appliances and has an island bar. Home was built in 2017 and has been maintained very well and continuously improved so its like new!  Perfect vacation spot for second home or short term rental with revenue projections available.  Storage shed behind home.  Driveway goes all the way through to alley.  Pre-wired security system with cameras.
